paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information for the TTR gene, including penetrance data.

patients.phenotype: Hereditary transthyretin amyloidosis (hATTR) with ocular manifestations

functional_data.summary: The TTR Val30Met variant is the most well-studied and prevalent in certain populations.

variants.segregation_data: The TTR variants are associated with hereditary amyloidosis.
variants.additional_notes: The study included various TTR variants, but specific penetrance data for individual variants was not provided.
key_quotes: Thirty patients had the TTR Val30Met variant; the remaining six patients had other variants (Ser50Arg, Asp38Ala, Tyr114His, Ser50Ile, Arg54Thr, and Phe53Val).

extraction_metadata.notes: No individual-level penetrance data was provided for specific variants.
